  <content type="text/html" mode="xml">
    <div xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><h2>Ingredients</h2>

<ul>
<li>450g tin of chopped tomatoes or pasatta sauce</li>
<li>100g gorgonzola</li>
<li>150g - 200g penne or other pasta</li>
</ul>

<h2>Method</h2>

<p>If using tinned tomatoes, put them in a blender and liquify. Heat over a medium flame.</p>

<p>Cook the penne, following the instructions on the packaging. </p>

<p>Chop the gorgonzola into 1/2 inch cubes. Drain the pasta. Put the pasta and gorgonzola in bowls. </p>

<p>Pour over the hot sauce. Garnish with a leaf of basil and some cracked black pepper.</p></div>
